EmailRemittanceAdvice is an ActionForm
    action is EmailRemittanceAdviceToVendor
    Layout
        single column
            PrmFromEmail
                show up to 100 characters
            PrmToEmail
                show up to 100 characters
            PrmCcEmail
                show up to 100 characters
            PrmEmailSubject
                show up to 100 characters
            paragraph
                PrmEmailTemplate
                    select is PayablesPaymentOutputIDMEmailTemplate
                button of "<PrmEmailTemplate.Name>"
                    link is external "<PrmEmailTemplate.RetrieveUrl>"
                    display as link
